    "Figure 8 clarifies the used model for the autoencoder.",
    "The plot in Fig. 9 shows the learning curve of the autoencoder model.",
    "The curve clarifies that the model achieves a good fit in the reconstruction process.",
    "3.3 The deep learning model for classification task Several metrics are used to evaluate the model performance including the following (i) Accuracy, (ii) Precision: calculate the proportion of samples that have been accurately categorized compared to all samples.",
